The paper discusses the use of deep reinforcement learning for autonomous driving, which involves complex state and action spaces in a continuous domain. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
